last_episode_to_air.name: 3 Chimps
last_episode_to_air.overview: On this episode, vets and keepers work together as they attempt a procedure that is rarely done at Taronga, putting three chimpanzees on the hospital operating table on the same day; Taronga staff teach a badly injured owl how to fly again.

name: Taronga: Who's Who In The Zoo
original_name: Taronga: Who's Who In The Zoo
overview: Join us at Taronga Zoo in Sydney for a new documentary series narrated by Naomi Watts. The series provides a look behind the scenes at what it takes to run one of the world's most famous and magnificent zoos.
